== audio ==

jack2-dbus 
 + dbus-python
qjackctl (make sure qjackctl is set to dbus mode)
alsa-plugins
alsa-utils (alsamixer)

/etc/asound.conf
===================

# use this as default
pcm.!default {
    type plug
    slave { pcm "jack" }
}

ctl.mixer0 {
    type hw
    card 1
}

# pcm type jack
pcm.jack {
    type jack
    playback_ports {
        0 system:playback_1
        1 system:playback_2
    }
    capture_ports {
        0 system:capture_1
        1 system:capture_2
    }
}

